<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1946-04-18T19:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1946-04-18T19:00:00-05:00" n="671" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d671">
                    <note rend="inline" type="source">560.AL/4–1846: Telegram</note>
                    <head>
                        <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                            Ambassador in the United Kingdom</hi> (<persName type="to"><hi rend="italic">Winant</hi></persName>)</head>
                    <opener>
                        <seg rendition="#left">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">secret</hi>
                            <lb/>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">u.s. urgent</hi>
                        </seg>
                        <dateline rendition="#right">
                            <placeName>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1946-04-18T19:00:00-05:00">April 18,
                                1946—7 p.m.</date>
                        </dateline>
                    </opener>
                    <p>3329. For Hawkins from Wilcox. Decision has been made to postpone negotiating
                        meeting until next year. No announcement being made by Department. Will send
                        you recommended program as soon as possible. [Wilcox.]</p>
                    <closer>
                        <signed>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Byrnes</hi>
                        </signed>
                    </closer>
                </div>
                </body></text></TEI>